| Aspect | Details |
|--------|---------|
| **Model** | Supabase/gte-small (384 dims) |
| **Library** | @xenova/transformers v2.17.2 |
| **Text Input** | Title + Body (space-separated) |
| **Max Input Length** | 6000 characters |
| **Preprocessing** | Whitespace normalization, trim, null check |
| **Storage - Posts** | `journals.embeddings` (pgvector) |
| **Storage - Stories** | `stories.embedding` (pgvector) |
| **Generated At** | Post creation, post update, story creation |
| **Caching** | 250 entries, 10-min TTL |
| **Index** | IVFFlat (cosine similarity) |
| **Usage** | Related posts discovery via `find_related_posts` RPC |

