### 6. Backend Service Logic

**File: C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\server\services\interactService.js (Line 238-362)**

**Function Signature:**
```javascript
export const repostService = async(sourceJournalId, caption, userId)
```

**Key Validations:**
1. Caption max 280 chars
2. Source post must be public
3. Cannot repost own posts
4. Prevents duplicate reposts of same source
5. Follows repost chains to ultimate original post

**Data Stored in DB:**
```javascript
.insert({
    user_id: userId,
    is_repost: true,
    repost_source_journal_id: ultimateSourceId,
    repost_caption: caption || null,
    post_type: 'text',
    content: null,
    title: repostTitle.length > 255 ? repostTitle.substring(0, 255) : repostTitle,
    privacy: 'public'
})
```

**Repost Title Format:** `"Repost: {original_post_title}"`

**Notification:** Creates repost notification for original post author (unless self)

**Return Value:**
```javascript
{message: 'repost created', repostId: insertedRepost.id, sourceJournalId: ultimateSourceId}
```

