```

### 3. RelatedPosts.jsx — RelatedPostCard action bar

Pass `onAddTake`, `onRepost`, `onSave`, and `currentUserId` as props.

Below `.rp-card-meta`, add an action bar:

```jsx
<div className="rp-card-actions">
    <button className="rp-action-btn" onClick={(e) => { e.stopPropagation(); onAddTake(post); }}>
        {/* pen/write SVG icon */}
        <span className="rp-action-label">Your take</span>
    </button>
    {post.user_id !== currentUserId && (
        <button className="rp-action-btn" onClick={(e) => { e.stopPropagation(); onRepost(post); }}>
            {/* repost SVG icon */}
            <span className="rp-action-label">Repost</span>
        </button>
    )}
    <button className="rp-action-btn" onClick={(e) => { e.stopPropagation(); onSave(post); }}>
        {/* bookmark SVG icon */}
        <span className="rp-action-label">Save</span>
    </button>
</div>
```

Each button uses `e.stopPropagation()` so clicking an action doesn't also navigate to the post.

SVG icons: small inline SVGs (16px), matching the existing icon style from PostCards/ContentView. Pen icon for "Your take", loop-arrows for "Repost", bookmark for "Save".

### 4. RelatedPosts.jsx — RepostModal + toast rendering

At the bottom of the `RelatedPosts` return, after `.rp-grid`:

```jsx
{repostJournal && (
    <RepostModal
        journal={repostJournal}
        onClose={(result) => {
            setRepostJournal(null);
            if (result === 'success') showToast('Post was reposted');
        }}
    />
)}

<AnimatePresence>
    {toast && (
        <motion.div className="rp-toast" initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 8 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }} exit={{ opacity: 0, y: 8 }} transition={{ duration: 0.2 }}>
            {toast}
        </motion.div>
    )}
</AnimatePresence>
```

